msgstr "Enable upload to online sources"

msgctxt "#39026"
msgid "When enabled, the Segment Editor shows Upload so you can submit segments to TheIntroDB.org and/or IntroDB.app. You still need valid API keys below."
msgstr "When enabled, the Segment Editor shows Upload so you can submit segments to TheIntroDB.org and/or IntroDB.app. You still need valid API keys below."

